  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink21-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> puṟattoḻukkam eṉakku iṉiyillai eṉṟu talaimakaṉ teḷippavum aḵtu uḷatu eṉṟu
          vēṟupaṭum talaimakaṭkut tōḻi colliyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink21">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> muḷḷi nīṭiya mutunī raṭaikaraip</l>
          <l> puḷḷik kaḷva ṉāmpa laṟukkun</l>
          <l> taṇṭuṟai yūraṉ ṟeḷippavu</l>
          <l> muṇkaṇ pacappa tevaṉko laṉṉāy.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> Although the man from the village by the cool ghat </l>
          <l rend='indent2'> where on the settling shore by the old water overgrown by Muḷḷi
            creepers</l>
          <l rend='indent2'> the spotted crab tears off the white lotus</l>
          <l> Explained [himself],</l>
          <l> My kajal eyes are becoming pale. What [is this], mother?</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
